  await Adapty().openWebPaywall(
    product: <YOUR_PRODUCT>,
    openIn: AdaptyWebPresentation.inAppBrowser,
  );
  // The web paywall will be opened in the in-app browser
} on AdaptyError catch (adaptyError) {
  // handle the error
} catch (e) {
  // handle other errors
}

```
